(31,	'Recenze Realme 12 Pro+: Ingredience výjimečného fotomobilu',	'<h1 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 7px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 40px; line-height: 45px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(201, 46, 72);\">Hardware</h1><h1 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 7px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 40px; line-height: 45px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(201, 46, 72);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); margin-bottom: 23px !important;\">Začneme u displeje, který se meziročně nezměnil. Je to výrazněji<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;zaoblený 6,7palcový AMOLED s Full HD rozlišením</span>, 120Hz frekv